//! Golden frame corpus + truncation + capability-skew tests (plan 045).
//!
//! Binary fixtures under `corpus/` are regenerated by the ignored
//! `regenerate_corpus` test. Exhaustive matches on `ClientFrame` /
//! `ServerFrame` force a fixture when a new variant is added.

#![expect(
    clippy::unwrap_used,
    clippy::panic,
    reason = "integration corpus tests"
)]

